    "CommitMsg": "fix: eliminate ReDoS patterns in ErrorSanitizationConfig regex\n\nReplace three regex patterns with catastrophic backtracking risk:\n- SELECT .+? FROM: use \\S+ alternation to avoid ambiguous quantifiers\n- WHERE .+? AND|OR: eliminate trailing \\s*$ alternation causing backtracking\n- ([REDACTED]\\s*)+: replace nested quantifier with non-capturing group\n\nFound by custom semgrep ReDoS rules (tests/security/rules/redos.yaml).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e",
